{"tid":1910850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山崎之後】請取消Citi/HSBC既「聲紋認證」！","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T01:00:10.000Z","uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c60490b64b811f0790c5c34001be6c4a50e71c5d","tid":1910850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"Citi  / HSBC前幾年推出「聲紋認證」，收集客戶既聲紋做識別。<br />\n<br />\n自從山崎麵包單野，大家應該思考下係咪要取消「聲紋」服務。係香港，軍政府最大最惡、又多奶共紅官。<br />\n<br />\n人地一聲令下，無論美資Citi、英資HSBC肯定會跪。<br />\n<br />\n你曾經發夢大叫「黑警死全家」，只要同銀行聲紋database一比對，就證明到你係發夢現場，好快就有狗搵到上門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家應該諗下係咪繼續用呢種生物認證服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n語音認證系統 &ndash; 花旗銀行(香港)<br />\n<br />\n    「聲紋」是根據每個人的聲道形狀、說話頻率和聲調等不同特徵所組成，能準確運用於各種通訊渠道如固網及手提電話中。<br />\n<br />\n    在得到您的同意下，我們的認證系統會將您的話音轉化成聲紋。 當您日後使用「電話理財服務」時，您的聲紋將成為核證身份的依據，確認程序迅速完成。<br />\n<br />\n登記或了解更多詳情，請致電(852) 2860 0345。"},{"pid":"4ae5a14f7337a725f6e7d5a80f62e0a2aa4cfbe3","tid":1910850,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">思覺脫早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4bd9c820fe2027d594674611cd0b2beeed5d778b","tid":1910850,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"另有HSBC link：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/ways-to-bank/phone/voice-id/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fways-to-bank%2Fphone%2Fvoice-id%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=f86253d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/ways-to-bank/phone/voice-id/</a>"},{"pid":"8b5695c18848c5adfa06443a09d771c85f9c6669","tid":1910850,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ae5a14f7337a725f6e7d5a80f62e0a2aa4cfbe3","tid":1910850,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":2,"s